data.description:
Welcome to your dream beachside haven. This retreat boasts an enviable corner lot location that perfectly encapsulates the essence of oceanside living. With three beautifully appointed bedrooms and two full bathrooms, this residence is tailored for relaxation and convenience.Embrace the Florida sunshine with a 2018-installed pool, featuring a sun shelf for leisurely lounging and a spacious deck with pavers, an enclosed screened area ensuring privacy and comfort. The expansive pavered driveway not only accommodates two cars within the attached garage but also offers additional space for guests or your watercraft.The fenced-in backyard is an oasis of outdoor enjoyment complete with a useful shed, ideal for storing all your beach gear, and a 50AMP RV/car outlet. Inside, the bright and airy kitchen invites culinary exploration with stone countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, and a functional island that provides extra storage and seating space.
Floors gleam with polished tile planks throughout, giving the home a modern and elegant touch. Fresh paint throughout and the bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated with vanities and fixtures, adding a touch of luxury. The enclosed patio not only serves as a laundry area but offers flexibility as a bonus bedroom or home office.
For your peace of mind, this home includes a new gas water heater, AC (2023), roof (2021) hurricane rated garage door, updated electrical panel 200 AMP service, as well as an irrigation well to keep your garden lush. Situated just steps from both the tranquil river and the vibrant beach, this home is a slice of paradise where every day feels like a vacation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this coastal gem your own and revel in the ultimate beachside lifestyle!
All information is intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.  Buyer to verify.
